To set up localhost in a particular directory:
1. php -S localhost:8080

How to install LAMP in ubuntu:

For installing apache
1. sudo apt-get update
2. sudo apt-get install apache2

for installation of MYSQL in ubuntu:
1. sudo apt-get install mysql-server
2. mysql_secure_installation

for installation of php:
1. sudo apt-get install php libapache2-mod-php php-mcrypt php-mysql
2. sudo systemctl restart apache2
3. sudo apt-get install php-cli

Reference:
https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-linux-apache-mysql-php-lamp-stack-on-ubuntu-16-04

